caller_intent: The caller wanted to speak with Holly Moore at Alliance Insurance but was informed she was unavailable until 10:30 AM.
resolution_steps: Agent informed caller that Holly Moore was unavailable until 10:30 AM.
Agent offered to leave a message for Holly or direct the caller to her voicemail.
summary: The caller attempted to reach Holly Moore but was informed she was unavailable. The agent offered to leave a message or direct the caller to voicemail. The call concluded with the caller agreeing to leave a message.
